item.title: Contact
item.description: Contact Pinterop is the one man company of me, Emanuel Palm. It is established in Alingsås and operates all over Sweden and beyond. To ask questions or book appointments, use emanuel [dot] palm [at] pinterop [dot] se or connect with me on LinkedIn. You should receive an answer within a day or two.
